scene.message:
Brown: Huh? Back in my world,{nl}
wasn't that guy the student{nl}
council president?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: A different person{nl}
became council president? A{nl}
wise choice.{waitkey}...Though there was no sign{nl}
an election was held...?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh, serves him right,{nl}
is what I say!{waitkey}The old council president was{nl}
all slick talk and apparently{nl}
never actually did a thing.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I didn't like the old{nl}
council president either. All{nl}
talk and so full of himself!{waitkey}{ret}

Officer: Not making me the{nl}
president — what are the{nl}
people at this school{nl}
thinking?!{waitkey}It was my dream to leave my{nl}
name in school history as a{nl}
great council president...!{waitkey}{ret}

President: Now that I'm{nl}
president, I'll make this a{nl}
fine, hardworking student{nl}
council!{waitkey}{ret}

Officer: The president's so{nl}
dedicated, it makes the rest{nl}
of us want to work hard too.{waitkey}{ret}

Officer: The president looks{nl}
up to a past council{nl}
president, apparently.{waitkey}Yamada, or some name like{nl}
that, I think it was.{waitkey}{ret}
